review_comments.body:
We don't need a separate call to rawService here.  We already have the history file contents present in the Result instance passed in to the map() method.  Just do something like (taken from JobHistoryRawService.getJobHistoryInputStreamFromResult()):

```
KeyValue keyValue = result.getColumnLatest(Constants.RAW_FAM_BYTES,
    Constants.JOBHISTORY_COL_BYTES);

byte[] historyFileContents = null;
if (keyValue == null) {
  throw new MissingColumnInResultException(Constants.RAW_FAM_BYTES,
      Constants.JOBHISTORY_COL_BYTES);
} else {
  historyFileContents = keyValue.getValue();
}
```

